WEBVTT

00:04:57.999 --> 00:05:00.283
that is actually teaching women

00:05:00.283 --> 00:05:02.154
how to do small business

00:05:02.154 --> 00:05:03.333
and how to carry the message

00:05:03.333 --> 00:05:05.976
of nutrition and hygiene.

00:05:05.976 --> 00:05:08.183
We have 60,000 such women

00:05:08.183 --> 00:05:10.035
now in India.

00:05:10.035 --> 00:05:12.488
It's not about selling soap,

00:05:12.488 --> 00:05:13.941
it's about making sure

00:05:13.941 --> 00:05:15.981
that in the process of doing so

00:05:15.981 --> 00:05:18.174
you can change people's lives.

00:05:18.174 --> 00:05:21.371
Small actions, big difference.

00:05:21.371 --> 00:05:23.090
Our R&amp;D folks

00:05:23.090 --> 00:05:26.719
are not only working to give us 
some fantastic detergents,

00:05:26.719 --> 00:05:29.488
but they're working to make sure we use less water.

00:05:29.488 --> 00:05:31.652
A product that we've just launched recently,